other_tests.findings: Scant superficial strips of inactive endometrium in a background of abundant mucus.
Densely hypercellular stroma without clear demarcation between the cortex and medulla; features consistent with ovarian hyperthecosis.
other_tests.changes_over_time: Three months after the procedure, the patient's total testosterone level decreased to less than 20 ng per deciliter, and estradiol level also decreased to less than 20 pg per milliliter.
